Zambia’s Annual Inflation Rate Slowed to 8.8% in April From 9.2% in March

-- B y   O b e r t   S i m w a n z a
-- 
2011-04-28T08:27:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-28/zambia-s-annual-inflation-rate-slowed-to-8-8-in-april-from-9-2-in-march.html
Zambia’s annual inflation rate fell
to 8.8 percent in April from 9.2 percent in the previous month,
the  Central Statistics Office  said in a statement handed to
reporters in the capital, Lusaka, today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nasreen Seria at 
 nseria@bloomberg.net  